{"tid":1638050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本18禁漫畫暗藏「香港加油」聲援彩蛋","createTime":"2019-10-08T07:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:37:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ac5af36562955c82d9e9e54318d4767163a4d07b","tid":1638050,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpAquA3S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpAquA3S.jpg&h=94d2c2aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牆壁上偷偷寫著「香港加油」。（圖擷自ハルカチャンネル ????紅楼夢Ｋ-16b推特）<br />\n<br />\n中國近來不斷「和諧化」網路和書籍內容，但近日有眼尖的網友發現，在日本「18禁」同人漫畫中，竟出現「香港加油、天安門64」字樣，原來是日本成人漫畫家為聲援香港反送中運動，而出的奇招。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpVkwNPg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpVkwNPg.jpg&h=7687651f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n酒瓶上印有「天安門64」字樣。（圖擷自ハルカチャンネル ????紅楼夢Ｋ-16b推特）<br />\n<br />\n 專營日本成人漫畫的推特貼文寫道「這是防止非法上傳的對策」，並附上兩張漫畫內容擷圖，「聲援彩蛋」就藏在酒瓶的標籤上印有「天安門64」和女主角背後的牆壁上寫著「香港加油」。<br />\n<br />\n有網友笑稱「漫畫界有漫畫界聲援的方法」、「應該放習近平小熊維尼浮水印上去才對」，還有專業網友爆料「曾有人把相關文宣夾在漫畫中間」，讓香港網友大讚「傑出的一手」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2939166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2939166&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNgmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=d13ca51a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2939166&h=d05eb83e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2939166</a>"},{"pid":"de080aeceefa3b3bae78648245c47934d053ffca","tid":1638050,"uid":304935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"大家都知道西方人好<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重視言論自由</span></span><br />\n所以,大家麻煩<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煲大火箭隊莫雷發表既言論</span></span><br />\n既然依家中國共產黨企到咁硬, 咁我地就<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">煲大佢!</span></span><br />\n將中國共產黨變成對人地既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國家安全威脅!</span></span><br />\n等全世界人都覺醒<br />\n將中國共產黨視為對西方文明既威脅!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有大陸人支持911事件!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯合抗共, 將全世界人民聯合起來, 反抗暴政!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">United We Stand, Divided We Fall!!!!!記住二戰果陣, 日本係點樣喚醒沉睡的巨人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有電競選手果單! 將呢兩件事變成西方憲政危機同國家安全威脅!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">莫雷, 電競, 支持911, 呢三件事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n傳開去, 感謝手足!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    祝<br />\n光復香港, 時代革命"},{"pid":"3d88370429ca0ec6b4f5bc1a353e6ad6808d9d06","tid":1638050,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299dd0d735e0b288bb16c334709e3933b5807cc3","tid":1638050,"uid":315335,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEgXopa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%